title: Baker Mayfield is Who the Browns Need
itunes:title: Baker Mayfield is Who the Browns Need
description:
The Good Morning Football Crew debates whether the Chargers are a Super Bowl contender (12:48). The gang also discusses what they learned from week 12 (24:59). Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Peter Schrager, and Kyle Brandt discuss AFC/NFC Wild Card teams (38:18). Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe! (49:43)
